properties.Desc_: Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme outer end, which is junction of Kjerulfs and Franz Josef Fjords. In background; Fraenkels Halfo, with mountains facing south over north entrance… July 31, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme out end. In background: Fraenkels Halvo, with mts. Facing south over north entrance to Kaiser Franz Josef Fjord… taken from bridge of SS Veslekari looking north. July 31, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme outer end. Detail of largest iceberg we saw in Kjerulfs Fjord. See photos; 19-A-17, 19-A-13, and 19-A-12*. Photo taken from bridge of SS Veslekari looking north. July 31, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme outer end. Detail of largest iceberg we saw in Kjerulfs Fjord. See photos; 19-A-9, 19-A-13, and 19-A-17*. Photo taken from bridge of SS Veslekari, looking north. July 31, 1931.

<NullKjerulfs Fjord. Extreme outer end. Detail of largest iceberg was saw in Kjerulfs Fjord. See photos; 19-A-12, 19-A-9, & 19-A-17*. Photo taken from bridge of Veslekari, looking north. July 31, 1931.>
Kjerulfs Fjord. Riddarbogen: this is the NW entrance. Photo taken from Veslekari, at anchor. Looking NW. July 31, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Riddarborgen: This is the NW entrance. Photo taken from Veslekari, at anchor. Looking NW. July 31, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Riddarborgen NW entrance of Kjerulfs Fjord and Kaiser Franz Josef Fjord, in background and very large bergs in foreground… taken from our launch en route to inner end. August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Riddarborgen NW entrance to Kjerulfs Fjord and Kaiser Franz Josef Fjord, in background and very large bergs in foreground… taken from our launch en route to inner end. August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Glacier. Western side - near where we anchored - just south of Riddarborgen at NW entrance. Photo taken from motorboat, looking west. August 3, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme outer end. In background; mountains forming east side of Kjerulfs Fjord. In foreground; one of the largest icebergs of the 530 we saw in Kjerulfs Fjord… July 31, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme outer end. In background; mountains forming east side of Kjerulfs Fjord. In foreground; one of the largest icebergs of the 530 we saw in Kjerulfs Fjord… July 31, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme outer end. In background; mountains forming east side of Kjerulfs Fjord. In foreground; one of the largest icebergs of the 530 we saw in Kjerulfs Fjord… July 31, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Very large icebergs which prevented taking Veslekari to inner end of fjord. In background: Fraenkels Halfo, with mountains on north side… August 3, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Glacier. Western side - near where we anchored - just south of Riddarborgen at NW entrance. Photo taken from motorboat, looking west. August 3, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Glacier. Western side - near where we anchored - just south of Riddarborgen at NW entrance. Photo taken from motorboat, looking west. August 3, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background on right L.A.B.'s Curry-comb Peak at junction of Left, Right, and Main Valleys. Its grooved side forms the west side of Left Valley… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Very large bergs which, with others, prevented Veslekari from going to inner end of fjord. August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. The bend, approaching from the north. In background mountains forming eastern side of fjord. The glacier faces NW. Foreground: western shore of fjord delta of sand… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. The bend, approaching from the north. In background mountains forming eastern side of fjord. The glacier faces NW. Foreground: western shore of fjord delta… August 1, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Looking N foreground; big delta (shown in 28-12*) at bend of fjord. Background: mountains and glaciers of Fraenkels Halvo facing S and overlooking Kaiser Franz Josef Fjord… Aug 1, 1931
Kjerulfs Fjord. In background; mountains forming eastern side of fjord. In foreground; large iceberg - seen at right in photo 28-12*. Photo taken from motorboat. August 3, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. Foreground: line of 55 stranded icebergs - none over 15 to 18 feet high. Back of these, on left, is range of mountains which form the eastern side… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. L.A.B.'s Curry-comb Peak at junction of Main, Left, and Right Valleys… We anchored launch just beyond berg shown. Photo taken from launch… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background on right; L.A.B.'s Curry-comb Peak with its glacier facing north over Right Valley and its deeply grooved sides, with snow patch… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Inner end looking NNE. This is the north end of L.A.B.'s Main Valley; arrow marks place where we left our motorboat on the west shore (left in photo)… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background; mountains forming eastern side of Kjerulfs Fjord: here seen at the extreme inner end of the fjord, at the NE end of Main Valley… Aug. 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Inner end. In background range of mountains forming eastern side of fjord. Below in fjord is line of stranded icebergs stretching across the fjord… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background on left southern terminal of range of mountains forming eastern side of Kjerulfs Fjord. From here mountains curve ENE… August 1, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background on left southern terminal of range of mountains forming eastern side of Kjerulfs Fjord. From here mountains curve ENE and form north side… Aug. 1 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Exteme inner end. Scoop Mountain, showing deep scoop of ice and snow over summit and very abrupt side facing north over Hisinger Glacier, which is seen below… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background on left Scoop Mountain and range of mountains forming eastern side of glacier, filling Unknown Valley… August 1, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. In background; west side of Hisinger glacier south of Left Valley, where it forms western (NW) side of that valley and has L.A.B.'s Curry-comb Peak… August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. In background; range of mountains forming western side of Hisinger Glacier at L.A.B.'s Divide. These mountains also form western side of Left Valley… August 6, 1931.

Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier, southern side, between Scoop Mountain and the inner end of Dickson Fjord, where the glacier ends… Photo taken on northern side of Scoop Mt., looking WNW. Aug. 6, 1931.
Kjerulfs-Dickson Fjords. In foreground Hisinger Glacier taken from south side above Dickson Fjord. In background, on left, "JFB" Mt. on west side of Left Valley and also looks through Left Valley…
Dickson Fjord. In background; range of mountains forming western side of Hisinger Glacier at L.A.B.'s Divide. They also from western side of Left Valley… August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. In background on right; Currycomb Peak and range of mountains along west side of Left Valley. In foreground: Hisinger coming from south in Unknown Valley… August 6, 1931.

Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier, south side, showing glacier reaching waters of Dickson Fjord at extreme inner end of fjord. In background; mountains forming north side of Dickson Fjord… Aug. 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. In background; range of mountains forming western side of Hisinger Glacier at L.A.B.'s Divide. They also form western side of Left Valley… Looking WNW. August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. In background on left; L.A.B.'s Currycomb Peak, showing side that is western side of Left Valley. In foreground at center; range of mountains forming northern side… August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background; western terminal of mountains forming north side of Dickson Fjord. - which is also the southern terminal of same range… August 6, 1931.

Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier, southern side, between Scoop Mountain and the inner end of Dickson Fjord, where the glacier ends… Photo taken on northern side of Scoop Mt., looking WNW. Aug. 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier at extreme inner end of Dickson Fjord. In background; mountains forming north side on Dickson Fjord… This photo taken from SW side of extreme inner end… Aug. 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier - south side. Stream - sources in glacier - descends over well worn rock formation along south side and flows into the head of Dickson Fjord… August 6, 1931.

Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier at extreme inner end of Dickson Fjord. In background; mountains forming north side of Dickson Fjord… This photo taken from SW side of extreme inner end… August 6, 1934.
Dickson Fjord, extreme inner end. In background; mountains forming north side of Dickson Fjord. In foreground; Hisinger Glacier. Photo taken from south side of Hisinger… August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background; western terminal of mountains forming north side of Dickson Fjord. - which is also the southern terminal of same range… August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background; mountains forming north side, above Hisinger Glacier, as it goes into Dickson Fjord. Photo taken from SW side of inner end… August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier. Photo taken of face of glacier at SW side of inner end of Dickson Fjord. August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier. Photo taken of face of glacier at SW side of inner end of Dickson Fjord. August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier. Photo taken of face of glacier at SW side of inner end of Dickson Fjord. August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier. Photo taken from south side near where glacier enters Dickson Fjord, looking NNW. August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier. Photo taken of face of glacier at SW side of inner end of Dickson Fjord. August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier. Photo taken of face of glacier at SW side of inner end of Dickson Fjord. August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier. Photo taken of face of glacier at SW side of inner end of Dickson Fjord. August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background; range of mountains forming western side of Left Valley, of which L.A.B.'s Curry-comb Peak is NW point… August 6, 1931.
Dickson Fjord. Hisinger Glacier, south side - to east of L.A.B.'s Scoop Mountain. In background; mountains forming western side of Hisinger Glacier and west side of Left Valley… August 6, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. High cliffs forming southern terminal of mountains which have formed eastern side of Kjerulfs Fjord. Photo taken on southern slope, looking NNW… Aug. 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. Extreme southern terminal of mountains which form east side of Kjerulfs Fjord. Photo taken looking overhead to the north… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord.
Through to Dickson Fjord. August 2, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background; north side of L.A.B.'s Scoop Mountain showing both scoops and part of double wishbone snow-patch, as seen in 26-H-11 & 22-D-5*… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background: L.A.B.'s Scoop Mountain is here shown with snow (or glacier) near summit and tongue-shaped glacier descending… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord… In background: Mt. range with ice-cap (which was the continuance of my Scoop Mt. range) forming the south side of Dickson Fjord… August 2, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. L.A.B.'s Curry-comb Peak facing Left Valley, showing close-up slope of the lower part. In foreground at bottom of photo, south bank of stream on Right Valley near mouth… August 1, 1931
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background on left Scoop Mountain and range of mountains forming eastern side of glacier, filing Unknown Valley… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background on left, southern terminal of range of mountains forming east side of Kjerulfs Fjord; also of Main Valley and Left, which are shown… August 1, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background on left, southern terminal of range of mountains forming east side of Kjerulfs Fjord; also on Main and Left Valleys, which are shown here… Aug. 1, 1931
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. Main Valley south end, at junction with Left Valley. Background: Left Valley and mouth of its stream which has its source in shallow pond-like lake… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. Main Valley, south end at junction with Left Valley. Background: Left Valley…See 24-F-11, 24-F-12, 24-F-5, 27-1-13 & 27-1-12*… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. L.A.B.'s grooved Curry-comb Peak, forming west side of Left Valley at junction with Right Valley. Summit glacier on right faces north, overlooking Right Valley… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end of Main Valley. Distant background shows Left Valley with its stream descending the right side… Photo taken looking SSE. August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end: "Right Valley" - south side - from eastern terminal. Showing glaciers and piled up earth like mine-dump. See photos 22-D-18 & 24-F-2*… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. At left in background is Right Valley, south side, with glaciers. See photo 24-F-2*. Peak in hollow is in Right Valley and has glacier going ESE… August 1, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. Right Valley, looking west. Mass of piled-up earth, greatly resembling the dump of a mine. Position: above stream, on south side, near mouth of stream… Aug. 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end: "Right Valley" - south side - from eastern terminal. Showing glaciers and piled up earth like mine-dump. See photos 22-D-18 & 24-F-2… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background on left; eastern side of Left Valley. This is formed by range of mountains extending south on eastern side of Kjerulfs Fjord… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. L.A.B.'s grooved Curry-comb Peak, forming west side of Left Valley at junction with Right Valley. Summit glacier on right faces north, overlooking Right Valley… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. Junction of streams of right and left valleys. In background (extreme left) is sloping side of innermost southern point of mountain range… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. Junction of streams of right and left valleys. In background (extreme left) is sloping side of innermost southern point of mountain range… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In foreground on left southern terminal of mountains forming eastern side of Kjerulfs Fjord. In background on right L.A.B.'s Scoop Mt… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background; range of mountains forming eastern side of Hisinger Glacier, seen south of L.A.B.'s Scoop Mountain. At base of mountain is glacier… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background on left southern terminal of mountains forming eastern side of Kjerulfs Fjord… at junction Right and Left Valley, looking SSE. August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. Junction of streams of Right and Left Valley. In background (extreme left) is sloping side of innermost southern point of mountain range… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. Right Valley looking west. Mass of piled-up earth, greatly resembling the dump of a mine… See also 24-F-2 and 23-E-3*. August 1, 1931
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. Right Valley looking west. Mass of piled-up earth, greatly resembling the dump of a mine. Position: above stream, on south side near mouth… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. Right Valley looking west. Mass of piled-up earth, greatly resembling the dump of a mine… See also 22-D-18, 24-F-2, and 23 E 3*. August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end Main Valley. Mountain range forming the eastern side of Kjerulfs Fjord; from their entrance at Kaiser Franz Josef Fjord these mountains continue… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end of Main Valley. Mountain range forming the eastern side of Kjerulfs Fjord; from their entrance at Kaiser Franz Josef Fjord these mountains continue… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. This is extreme south end of mountains forming eastern side of Kjerulfs Fjord. Photo taken from slope below. See 36-3, 36-4, 36-2*. August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. In foreground on left southern terminal of mountains forming eastern side Kjerulfs Fjord… Left, Right, and Main Valleys looking SE. August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. On left southern end of mountains forming east side of Kjerulfs Fjord, Main Valley and Left Valley. Here they are seen curving east to continue… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. Western side of Scoop Mountain above banks of stream and not far from Right Valley are piles of earth resembling mine dumps… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Left Valley. In background: L.A.B.'s Currycomb Peak forming west side. In foreground on extreme left; mound of dirt. This is moraine from one of the points… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end, looking out of the fjord. Background on left: mountains forming western side of Kjerulfs Fjord, with the Menzies' fire of August… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord; inner end. Mountains forming western side of Kjerulfs, here form western side of Main Valley. This photo is no. 11 in pan A…. August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. The bend, approaching from the north. In background mountains forming eastern side of fjord. The glacier faces NW. Foreground: western shore of fjord delta of sand… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Inner end looking north. This is the north end of L.A.B.'s Main Valley; arrow marking place where we left our motorboat on the west shore (left in photo)… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end overloking the floor of Main Valley, with innumerable small waterways flowing down the scarcely perceptible decline of the valley floor… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end overlooking the floor of Main Valley, with innumerable small waterways flowing down the scarcely perceptible decline of the valley floor… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Inner end. In background range of mountains forming eastern side of fjord. Below in fjord is line of stranded icebergs stretching across the fjord… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Exteme inner end. Scoop Mountain, showing deep scoop of ice and snow over summit and very abrupt side facing north over Hisinger Glacier, which is seen below… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end overlooking the floor of Main Valley, with innumerable small waterways flowing down the scarcely perceptible decline of the valley floor… August 1, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Mountains forming eastern side; waterfalls descending from above, over black formation. See 36-2; 36-3; 36-4*. August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background; mountains forming western side of Kjerulfs Fjord are here seen on western side of Main Valley… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background; mountains forming western side of Kjerulfs Fjord are here seen on western side of Main Valley… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end looking north out of fjord. In background; mountains of eastern side of fjord showing at their base small icebergs in the fjord… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Extreme inner end looking north out of fjord. In background; mountains of eastern side of fjord showing at their base small icebergs in the fjord… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord, the inner end mountains forming western side of Kjerulfs Fjord. Here they form western side of Main Valley… August 2, 1931.
Through to Dickson Fjord.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background on left; mountains forming west side of Kjerulfs Fjord; here seen on west side of Main Valley… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background; NE terminal of mountains forming north side of Right Valley; here seen turning north… This photo is no. 2 in pan E. August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background: southern terminal of mountains forming west side of Kjerulfs Fjord. Mountains shown here as they turn west… August 2, 1931.
Through to Dickson Fjord.
Through to Dickson Fjord.
Kjerulfs Fjord. L.A.B.'s Curry-comb Peak, grooved sides facing Left Valley. Glaciers facing Right Valley. Junction of all three valleys… This photo is no. 3 in pan A. August 2, 1931.
Through to Dickson Fjord.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. Huge bolders [sic] on eastern side of "Left Valley." On right is western side of "Left Valley"… Photo taken on eastern side, near junction… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. Right Valley (general direction east and west). In background on right of photo is eastern terminal of range of mountains on the north side… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background: Right Valley. Glacier descends north side towards western end. Range faces south and here is shown reaching its NE terminal… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. L.A.B.'s Curry-comb Peak, grooved sides forming west side of Left Valley. In background on right mountain range of Curry-comb Peak, forming south side of Left Valley… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background; L.A.B.'s Curry-comb Peak, forming west side of Left Valley. On side of mountain are piles of earth like mine-dumps… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. Currycomb Peak at NW end of Left Valley. At bottom of photo, stream descending Left Valley. Photo taken from east side of Left Valley… August 2, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. In background on left, Currycomb Peak on west side of Left Valley, which is also seen. In right, background mountains, with snow and ice-cap, forming the north side of… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord.
Kjerulfs Fjord. L.A.B.'s Curry-comb Peak - the highest part of this mountain which overlooks the west side of Left Valley. Noticeable is the great erosion towards the summit… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. L.A.B.'s Curry-comb Peak, near extreme inner (southern) end of Left Valley; grooved sides form west side of Left Valley… This is no. 6 in pan D. August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background southern terminal of mountains forming western side of Kjerulfs Fjord, including Main Valley… Direction: looking NW. August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Right Valley looking west from its most eastern point. In foreground, mouth of stream of Left Valley, showing ravine (almost gorge) down which stream flows. August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. In background on left Curry-comb Peak on west side of Left Valley, which is also shown… This is no. 23 in Pan C. August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background; range of mountains forming north side of Right Valley are here shown turning north from the south end of the range of mountains… Aug. 2, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background on left southern terminal of mountains forming western side of Kjerulfs Fjord… photo is sequel to 24-F-19, also 27-1-9 & 27-1-8. August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background: rising above the glacier can be seen a peak or high nunatak. It may be an outstanding peak of another range… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background mountains on west side of Left Valley at SE end. In foreground Hisinger Glacier reaches its most northern point… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background mountains forming western side of Hisingers Glacier in Unknown Valley. Here they start to become the western side… August 2, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background mountains forming western side of Hisinger Glacier in Unknown Valley. Here they start to become the western side of Left Valley… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background on left: Curry-comb Peak forming west side of Left Valley. In background on right; mountains forming north side of Right Valley… Aug. 2, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. High cliffs forming southern terminal of mountains which have formed eastern side of Kjerulfs Fjord. Photo taken on southern slope, looking NNW… Aug. 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background; range of mountains forming (from this point south) the eastern side of Hisinger Glacier… This photo is no. 3 in pan II. August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. Extreme inner end. In background: L.A.B.'s Scoop Mountain shown here on the left, coming from NE where it has formed S side of Dickson Fjord… Aug. 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background on left, L.A.B.'s Scoop Mountain and the range of mountains forming (from this point south) the eastern side of Hisinger Glacier… Aug. 2, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background mountains forming western side of Hisinger Glacier in Unknown Valley. Here they start to become the western side… August 2, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background mountains on west side of Left Valley at SE end. In foreground: Hisinger Glacier (covered with sharp pointed hummocks…)… Aug. 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. Extreme southern terminal of mountains which form east side of Kjerulfs Fjord. Photo taken looking overhead to the north… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. High cliffs forming southern terminal of mountains which have formed eastern side of Kjerulfs Fjord. Photo taken on southern slope looking N… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. Extreme southern terminal of mountains which form east side of Kjerulfs Fjord. Photo taken looking overhead to the north… August 2, 1931.

Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background mountains forming western side of Hisinger Glacier in Unknown Valley. Here they start to become the western side of Left Valley… August 2, 1931.
Kjerulfs Fjord. Through to Dickson Fjord. In background mountains forming western side of Hisinger Glacier in Unknown Valley. Here they start to become the western side of Left Valley… Aug. 2, 1931.
